Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.33,0:21:08.03,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tu nič nie je, iba les.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:12.14,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Miharu naozaj nevieš vôbec nič, čo?
