Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.11,0:21:40.67,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keď nepôjdeme po ceste, tak sa nikdy nedostaneme z lesa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.67,0:21:42.65,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takže ma nasledujte...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.64,0:21:44.66,Main Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
